data.title: Emma Forbes
data.meta_description: Emma Forbes. Actress: Scrooge: A Christmas Sarah. Emma Forbes was born on 14 May 1965 in London, England, UK. She is an actress, known for Scrooge: A Christmas Sarah (1990), Alles Glück dieser Erde (1978) and Press Gang (1989). She has been married to Graham Clempson since September 1987. They have two children.
